"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-22-team-gb-olympic-hero-alex-yee-responds-criticism-celebration-upset-hayden-wilde-21467562\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Team GBstar Alex Yee insists he and his rivals are 'fierce' competitors but remain 'mates' after his celebration in supertri's opening race received a wave of criticism on social media.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 185, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12, \"end\": 20, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alex Yee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Yee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yee produced one of the standout moments of thissummer'sOlympic Gamesfrom a British perspective as hemounted an incredible comeback to pip New Zealand's Hayden Wilde to men's triathlon goldinParis.\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 384, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 263, \"end\": 270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9923903178793347, \"rank\": 0.007597094368706989, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 326, \"end\": 337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.9958711626204231, \"rank\": 0.003573908386101435, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\"}, {\"begin\": 347, \"end\": 352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olivia_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9701279970803535, \"rank\": 0.0307916477622269, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olivia_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olivia_Wilde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And on Sunday, history repeated itself as Yee - renowned for his prowess in the 10km run - once again overtook the Kiwi at the death to secure an outstanding victory in front of a rapturous Boston crowd.\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 501, \"end\": 505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.9995110954527624, \"rank\": 0.0004891004369773669, \"text\": \"Kiwi\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\"}, {\"begin\": 576, \"end\": 582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Red_Sox\", \"score\": 0.7664031224207114, \"rank\": 0.30464732939930866, \"text\": \"Boston\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Red_Sox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Red_Sox\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While approaching the finish line, the 26-year-old began thumping his chest before showboating with a Kylian Mbappe-like, arms-crossed celebration, which appeared to irk Wilde, who was left trailing in his wake.\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 802, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 761, \"end\": 766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olivia_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9701279970803535, \"rank\": 0.0307916477622269, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olivia_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olivia_Wilde\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yee's celebration received a mixed reaction among triathlon fans, withsome suggesting the Lewisham-born athlete had tarnished his win with the 'classless' and 'arrogant' stunt.\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 980, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Responding to the backlash on X at the time, Yee tweeted:\\u00a0'No celebration next time, apologies.'\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 1078, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wilde, meanwhile, said: 'I think I have been seeing too many silvers in the last couple of weeks so it would be nice to get a gold.'\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1212, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This weekend, Wilde will be looking to get revenge as the stars of supertri reconvene for the second meeting of the season in Chicago.\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1348, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1228, \"end\": 1233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olivia_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9701279970803535, \"rank\": 0.0307916477622269, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olivia_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olivia_Wilde\"}, {\"begin\": 1340, \"end\": 1347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\", \"score\": 0.999979399260896, \"rank\": 1.5805299241136253e-05, \"text\": \"Chicago\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a message on Instagram ahead of the race, Yee said he and his rivals were looking forward to 'putting on a show' in the Windy City.\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1366, \"end\": 1375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.32742448265497e-25, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Brit also reassured fans that he and Wilde remained good friends despite his showboating in Boston last time out.\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1527, \"end\": 1532, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olivia_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9701279970803535, \"rank\": 0.0307916477622269, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olivia_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olivia_Wilde\"}, {\"begin\": 1582, \"end\": 1588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Red_Sox\", \"score\": 0.7664031224207114, \"rank\": 0.30464732939930866, \"text\": \"Boston\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Red_Sox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Red_Sox\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We live for this sport,' Yee told his followers onInstagram.\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1666, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'After the Olympics I have ridden a rollercoaster.\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1718, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Incredible highs but also some lows too\\u2026 So to be able to race these guys again was pure excitement.\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1819, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'We race fiercely and competitively but at the end of the day we all are mates and want to put on a show for you.\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1934, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Thanks Boston!\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 1951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1944, \"end\": 1950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Red_Sox\", \"score\": 0.7664031224207114, \"rank\": 0.30464732939930866, \"text\": \"Boston\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Red_Sox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Red_Sox\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"#mbappe or #palmer.'\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 1972, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wilde accused his fellow competitors of 'hiding' and giving Yee an easy ride with their questionable tactics in Boston.\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 2093, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2086, \"end\": 2092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Red_Sox\", \"score\": 0.7664031224207114, \"rank\": 0.30464732939930866, \"text\": \"Boston\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Red_Sox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Red_Sox\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was just a bit of a shame the other boys did not decide to come and do some work, yeah they were just hiding a bit and waiting for the run,' he said.\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2248, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I do not really see that as racing, I was trying to call them through but they did not want to go through and if I did not keep pushing, the other boys [the chase group] would have turned up.\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2442, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's a bit of a shame to be honest but that's racing, that's their tactics and we will come into Chicago and try and get the win there.'\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2581, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2542, \"end\": 2549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\", \"score\": 0.999979399260896, \"rank\": 1.5805299241136253e-05, \"text\": \"Chicago\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chicago\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2631, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2633, \"to\": 2703, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:The Premier League is back but football's all the sweeter if you give something else a chance too  ArrowMORE:Olympic defector responds to critics as he faces two-year ban after Team GB switch  ArrowMORE:Olympics are relentless and exhausting, but I would have crawled onto the pitch to play  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 3117, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2719, \"end\": 2733, \